descriptionHtml:
This is my first Vanilla playthrough character. Since I\'m starting a new character with a heavily modded game, I thought to upload this one. There are 3 safe files. One in Whiterun Home (main HQ with all items), Windhelm Home (where my wife lives) and ontop of the throat of the world. There\'s tons of items placed in Barrels around the Smithery in Whiterun. I just felt like it\'s time to start a new character and abandone this one. Enjoy or use for testing purposes.

- On a special note: I\'ve used a plugin for SKSE that doubles gained perks...you can use the savegames without the plugin, with the benefit, that your perks are much higher then they normally would -
